      "why_text": "A single 1,000-unit EV order in Belgium signals that corporate and government fleet procurement is quietly becoming the backbone of European EV adoption \u2014 not the individual luxury buyer everyone keeps marketing to. For BMW, this validates its EV lineup as a fleet-grade product, not just a showroom statement, which carries serious long-term volume implications. It also puts pressure on Mercedes and Audi to match fleet credibility, not just spec sheets.",
