      "why_text": "The G-Wagon \u2014 one of the most status-loaded vehicles on the planet \u2014 has just gone electric with the G 580, and it arrives at a moment when BMW is proving legacy automakers can actually win the EV range game. Mercedes is betting that G-Wagon buyers, who've never cared about fuel economy, will now flex a different kind of excess: a six-figure electric off-roader that can spin on its own axis using torque vectoring. It's less about saving the planet and more about redefining what obscene luxury looks like in the EV era.",
