      "picks_file": "picks/picks-2026-06-07-0140.md",
      "why_text": "Puth's emotional public reaction \u2014 'heartbroken,' 'devastated' \u2014 signals just how much this tour means to him at a career moment when he's been working hard to reassert himself as a serious live act. Concert cancellations always sting fans who've traveled and planned, but the Orlando market is a high-stakes stop and the language he's using suggests this isn't a minor setback. It's a reminder of how physically brutal touring is, and how quickly an artist's momentum can be interrupted by something completely out of their control.",
